OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain, initially persistent with some
OL,7,Fheavier bursts, will gradually weaken
OL,8,Fovernight to leave a cloudy, damp
OL,9,Fstart to Tuesday, with hill fog across
OL,10,Fthe Pennines. Winds remaining light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FGradually brightening after a
OL,13,Fcloudy, damp start, and eventually
OL,14,Ffeeling warmer. However, thicker cloud
OL,15,Fand rain returning from the west
OL,16,Fthrough the evening. Turning breezier
OL,17,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
